      "widgets_values": [
        "=== 24GB RTX 4090 OPTIMIZATIONS ===\n\nBlockSwap: 28/40 blocks swapped to CPU RAM\n(was 10 — now swaps 70% of transformer blocks)\n\noffload_img_emb: TRUE (saves ~1.5GB)\noffload_txt_emb: TRUE (saves ~1GB)\n\nCLIP device: CPU (saves ~5GB VRAM)\n\nFrames: reduced from 88 → 49\n(88 frames OOMs on 24GB; 49 is safe)\nAfter RIFE 21→30fps interp, output is still smooth.\n\nmotion_amplitude: 1.0 (was 1.2, slightly reduced\nto keep face stable across frames)\n\n=== FACE CONSISTENCY SETUP ===\n\nTwo ImageLoaders:\n1. 'Face Image Loader' (node 262) — your AI face\n   → CLIPVisionEncode → PainterI2V clip_vision_output\n2. 'Scene / Start Frame Loader' (node 252) — scene\n   → ImageResize → PainterI2V start_image\n\nFor best results: use the same face image in both\nloaders, or use face as Face Loader and a\ncomposited scene as Start Frame.\n\nRequires: clip_vision_h.safetensors in\nyour models/clip_vision/ folder."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    }
